>\n海南雞飯 唔係跟文昌雞先既咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:01:08.000Z","msg":"準確啲來講就應該係新加坡或馬來西亞嘅海南人創造出海南雞飯呢套食物。可以留意一點嘅係，30/40年前嘅海南島根本就冇「海南雞飯」，係最近呢20年海南雞飯開始出名先引入去海南島。而且海南雞飯所採用嘅材料具有濃烈嘅南洋特色，例如用大量南洋香料同新馬獨有嘅走地雞，根本就好難喺海南島搵得齊。所以可以話係海南島原本有文昌雞嘅呢樣食物，但係成套海南雞飯嘅做法就應該係新馬地區形成同發揚光大"},{"pid":"be2a2a8afd2ca86b303a8d974bdb4a5d316162ca","tid":2498023,"uid":59602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:01:30.000Z","msg":"去武漢就索兩啖肺炎"},{"pid":"a8b32ef943fd57c9ec16a26dd60926fde53c7f3b","tid":2498023,"uid":299164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:01:41.000Z","msg":"海南島係文昌雞，唔係香港食開嘅星馬海南雞~<br />\n.文昌雞，又名蔡氏雞，是廣東八大優良雞種之一，N最早見於清代；亦為菜名，是海南四大名菜之一，因產地在海南省文昌市潭牛鎮而得名。傳統文昌雞的外型總括為「三小兩短」，即頭小、頸小、腳小、頸短、腳短。文昌雞的飼養與一般雞種最主要的分別，在於當地人就地取材，使用椰子來餵雞。"},{"pid":"e39b70c0b65cd9574da595b1c921374300f25945","tid":2498023,"uid":25424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0337d767f47775e3e665dd45c7fb5e599102271d","tid":2498023,"uid":2785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ea7968b4e6b7bc2e442f8763f470a702adb03f8e","tid":2498023,"uid":351978,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T01:53:25.000Z","msg":"佢真係衝出嚟㗎喎<br />\n海南雞飯都唔係喺海南島創造出來，新馬泰先係海南雞飯嘅發源地<br />\n下次佢去揚州開會，又會唔會話好想要香港青年去揚州食揚州炒飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T01:55:47.000Z","msg":"真心唔識 睇wiki<br />\n<br />\n海南雞飯是一道雞肉配香飯的瓊菜，作法起源於<span class=\"red\">海南島文昌縣</span>的家常飲食[1]，在海南當地，人人稱之為「文昌雞飯」，20世紀初期，移民到東南亞馬來亞、新加坡等地的海南人將海南雞飯帶到當地，並開始成功的商業化普及推廣，成為東南亞最著名的華人料理之一。海南人將其列爲海南四大名菜[2]之一的文昌當地出產的文昌鷄的白斬雞做法，配上利用雞油和雞湯所烹煮的米飯。20世紀初期，隨著移民潮，這個菜式傳至東南亞等地。[3] 它被認為是新加坡的國菜之一，最常與新加坡料理聯繫在一起，然而在整個東南亞，尤其是馬來西亞、泰國、印尼和汶萊的華人社區，都可見到海南雞飯的蹤跡。<br />\n<br />\n海南雞飯 唔係跟文昌雞先既咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:01:43.000Z","msg":"唐文化傳去日本生根發陽光大<br />\n<br />\n所以日本文化就係中国文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日本人就住中国人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f05396a4be73b8d25d9d9cf0f72ad46f153f1371","tid":2498023,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:01:48.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不如話椰子雞"},{"pid":"368c93be51d0c4cda2ad23e77d846c271c52edc3","tid":2498023,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5b3284e808372d913af9477b16d1565fd8ffc43","tid":2498023,"uid":22701,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T01:44:28.000Z","msg":"無知唔駛同全世界人講㗎屌你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:01:49.000Z","msg":"好彩個傻鳩會議都係得班傻鳩奶共人士去<br />\n如果唔係真係柒出國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f7c421c306a9edc3d02d79b1eb131d6da3fb076","tid":2498023,"uid":55759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:02:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />海南島係食文昌雞"},{"pid":"baf6c1fe6c7cd556e162ee97c5dd42e8e5081be0","tid":2498023,"uid":319512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5180a762f4494bb1265eb52efd0c5a7a405fc80a","tid":2498023,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T01:40:56.000Z","msg":"今年已經是我第三次出席博鰲亞洲論壇，適逢是論壇成立20周年，也是在全球疫情下一個難得的大規模線下活動，我除了出席論壇開幕禮和參與研討會外，也跟海南省領導和多個部委的老朋友見面。他們都不約而同向我問好，表達了對香港的親切關懷和對特區在國家安全有保障及完善選舉制度下的前景充滿信心。<br />\n<br />\n其中海南省領導得悉我們在粵港澳大灣區開展的青年就業和青年創業計劃，就主動提出在海南為香港青年提供就業和創業機會，並安排所需的配套，令我和同事都很感動。事實上，海南島天然環境好、農產豐富、人民好客熱情，近年在中央的大力支持下，正全面發展為自由貿易港；香港是海南的重要外資來源地，我們不難找到在香港和海南都有業務的企業為青年提供就業機會。<br />\n<br />\n我希望很快見到香港青年到海南實習、就業、創業，享受椰林樹影和港人喜愛的海南雞飯！<br />\n<br />\n#博鰲亞洲論壇 #BoaoForumForAsia #林鄭月娥 #CarrieLam<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K6cHvPR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK6cHvPR.jpg&h=51e24c76&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:02:30.000Z","msg":"佢真係唔識，佢嘅文膽都係弱智 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95e492352f0c9e7f80a10d2f443c3bbbc7cb116","tid":2498023,"uid":71393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:03:02.000Z","msg":"海南雞飯喺海南島?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新加坡人一定好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"678751849589ac9ee402a03554bd5fc58a59589b","tid":2498023,"uid":288765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:03:07.000Z","msg":"海藍雞手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1468d1a4fe30d59d0ac15062f7ffb784bc7287b","tid":2498023,"uid":59929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:03:07.000Z","msg":"海南雞 係海南人移居馬拉創出黎<br />\n點都唔算海南島菜式<br />\n即係港式蛋撻奶茶文化係英國傳入黎但蛋撻奶茶絕對唔係英國菜<br />\n咁所有人源自非洲我地都唔係非洲人<br />\n佢真係唔識架喎"},{"pid":"57ebdb05ba35f8897173cd553221e348a4e16af8","tid":2498023,"uid":147367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:03:12.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好比佢去瑞士<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a56850e96d40b4f56c3f01ea78a14412f3457dff","tid":2498023,"uid":218219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57ebdb05ba35f8897173cd553221e348a4e16af8","tid":2498023,"uid":147367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:03:12.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好比佢去瑞士<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:03:30.000Z","msg":"雞翼好食"},{"pid":"2f50a59cfe4c749da36f754edbd7fcc7b71d6f47","tid":2498023,"uid":40925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e3ad2b3a2fe22198ed75ac4096c3de26c4a7820","tid":2498023,"uid":106604,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"962c036d3685972dfe41fc4921cd20627331d94b","tid":2498023,"uid":53062,"like":68,"dislike":1,"score":67,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T01:43:11.000Z","msg":"海南雞飯唔係泰國 馬來西亞 新加坡創造？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T01:59:04.000Z","msg":"係邊個唔知<br />\n但一定唔係海南島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:04:34.000Z","msg":"一定係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1a449ed64d823d9a7d3c454089d2a51dc2be1f","tid":2498023,"uid":37976,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9a4710cfb7cd0f28d953125ce536fabbeacd25a","tid":2498023,"uid":12599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f1855403216e5c814547c3e6df730794ed894c09","tid":2498023,"uid":22701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc9ee0d92792c7c14488ee7a4cf8fe369b7235f6","tid":2498023,"uid":321977,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T01:44:05.000Z","msg":"其實海南雞飯係新加坡出名啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T01:46:30.000Z","msg":"咩為知出名啲？你覺得海南雞飯係海南島創？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T01:51:40.000Z","msg":"海南島無我哋認知嘅海南雞食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:04:39.000Z","msg":"我係海南食過喎 真係幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\